title: Here's a list of popular PHP frameworks
content: Laravel is one of the most popular frameworks.  Others include Symfony, CodeIgniter and CakePHP.

title: Here's a list of popular Python frameworks
content: Django is one of the most popular frameworks.  Others include Web2Py, Flask, Bottle and CherryPy.

title: Here's a list of popular CSS frameworks
content: Bootstrap is a very popular CSS frameworks.  Others include Tailwind CSS, Drawbacks and Bluma.
